<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Ship's Burguer | Năo é só sobre burger. É sobre história.</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rye&family=Oswald:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Roboto+Slab:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <style>
:root {
    --blue: #0f4ea2;
    --blue-dark: #082f68;
    --black: #111111;
    --ink: #202020;
    --paper: #f7f1e7;
    --paper-soft: #fffaf0;
    --line: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.2);
    --shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.12);
    --radius: 8px;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; overflow-x: hidden; }

  body {
    overflow-x: hidden;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: "Open Sans", Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-rendering: geometricPrecision;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(15, 78, 162, 0.06) 0 1px, transparent 1px),
      radial-gradient(circle at 74% 34%, rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.04) 0 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7), rgba(247, 241, 231, 0.92)),
      var(--paper);
    background-size: 18px 18px, 24px 24px, auto, auto;
  }

  body.menu-open { overflow: hidden; }
  img { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

  .container { width: min(1160px, calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; }

  .site-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 20;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--black);
    background: rgba(247, 241, 231, 0.96);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .header-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    min-height: 92px;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .brand { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; flex: 0 0 auto; min-width: 0; }

  .logo-complete {
    display: block;
    height: 78px;
    width: auto;
    max-width: 250px;
    object-fit: contain;
    object-position: left center;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    filter: contrast(1.08) saturate(1.05);
  }

  .brand-logo-fallback { display: none; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .brand-logo-fallback img { width: 70px; height: 70px; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 16%; border: 2px solid var(--blue); border-radius: 50%; background: var(--paper-soft); }
  .brand-text { display: grid; line-height: 0.9; }
  .brand-name { color: var(--black); font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif; font-size: clamp(2.15rem, 4vw, 3.25rem); line-height: .82; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .brand-subtitle { color: var(--blue); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: 1.08rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .brand-since { color: var(--black); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }

  .nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; gap: clamp(14px, 2.2vw, 32px); width: 100%; font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .nav a { color: var(--black); font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 1px; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent; transition: color .18s ease, border-color .18s ease; white-space: nowrap; }
  .nav a:hover, .nav a:focus-visible { color: var(--blue); border-color: var(--blue); outline: none; }

  .retro-button, .nav .order-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border: 2px solid var(--blue);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    color: var(--blue);
    background: transparent;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--black);
    font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease, background .18s ease, color .18s ease;
  }

  .retro-button:hover, .retro-button:focus-visible, .nav .order-link:hover, .nav .order-link:focus-visible {
    color: var(--paper-soft);
    background: var(--blue);
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--black);
    transform: translate(2px, 2px);
    outline: none;
  }

  .menu-toggle { display: none; width: 48px; min-width: 48px; height: 48px; border: 2px solid var(--black); border-radius: var(--radius); background: var(--paper-soft); color: var(--black); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; }

  .hero { position: relative; padding: clamp(42px, 7vw, 88px) 0 30px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--line); overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, .86fr) minmax(420px, 1.14fr); align-items: end; gap: clamp(18px, 3.5vw, 48px); }
  .eyebrow, .section-kicker { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; color: var(--blue); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: .98rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .eyebrow { justify-content: flex-start; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .eyebrow::before, .eyebrow::after { content: ""; width: 42px; height: 2px; background: var(--blue); }
  .section-kicker::before, .section-kicker::after { content: "*"; font-size: .9rem; }

  h1, h2, h3 { color: var(--black); font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif; line-height: .95; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 400; }
  h1 { max-width: 700px; font-size: clamp(4.25rem, 9.5vw, 8rem); letter-spacing: 2.5px; }
  h1 span, .section-title span { color: var(--blue); }
  .hero-copy { font-size: .98rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }
  .hero-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; min-height: 46px; padding: 9px 16px; border-top: 2px solid var(--black); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--black); color: var(--black); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: .98rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }

  .hero-plate { position: relative; min-height: 520px; isolation: isolate; background: transparent; border: none; box-shadow: none; overflow: visible; }
  .hero-plate::before { content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 7% 1% 14% 4%; z-index: -2; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(15, 78, 162, .24) 0 1.4px, transparent 1.5px); background-size: 12px 12px; transform: rotate(-2deg); pointer-events: none; }
  .hero-image-wrap { position: absolute; right: -76px; bottom: -18px; width: min(820px, 122%); height: min(560px, 84vw); background: transparent; border: none; box-shadow: none; overflow: visible; }
  .hero-image-wrap .hero-main-image { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; object-position: right bottom; background: transparent; border: none; box-shadow: none; mix-blend-mode: multiply; filter: contrast(1.08) saturate(1.05); }
  .hero-image-wrap::after { content: ""; position: absolute; left: 12%; right: 2%; bottom: 1%; height: 15%; z-index: -1; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(17,17,17,.20) 0%, rgba(17,17,17,.10) 42%, transparent 72%); filter: blur(5px); transform: scaleX(.92); pointer-events: none; }

  .section { padding: clamp(56px, 7vw, 88px) 0; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--line); }
  .section-heading { display: grid; place-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 36px; text-align: center; }
  .section-title { font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 11vw, 3.35rem); letter-spacing: 1px; }

  .timeline { position: relative; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 22px; margin-top: 28px; }
  .timeline::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: 56px; right: 8%; left: 8%; height: 3px; background: var(--blue); }
  .timeline-item { position: relative; display: grid; justify-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 0 10px; text-align: center; }
  .timeline-icon { display: grid; place-items: center; width: 112px; height: 112px; border: 3px solid var(--blue); border-radius: 50%; background: var(--paper-soft); color: var(--black); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; z-index: 1; }
  .timeline-year { color: var(--blue); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: .95; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .timeline-item h3 { font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: 1.45rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .timeline-item p { max-width: 240px; font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif; font-size: .98rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.55; }

  .products-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 18px; }
  .product-card { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 45% 1fr; min-height: 286px; border: 2px solid var(--blue); border-radius: var(--radius); background: rgba(255,250,240,.76); box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 rgba(17,17,17,.14); overflow: hidden; }
  .product-media { display: grid; place-items: end center; min-height: 250px; padding: 14px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.58), rgba(15,78,162,.08)); }
  .product-media img { width: 100%; height: 220px; object-fit: contain; filter: drop-shadow(0 12px 10px rgba(17,17,17,.22)); }
  .product-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; padding: 22px 18px 22px 6px; }
  .product-info h3 { font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 2.6vw, 2.15rem); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.05; }
  .product-info p { color: #303030; font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif; font-size: .96rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.6; }
  .price { color: var(--blue); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: 1.95rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1; }
  .product-info .retro-button { align-self: flex-start; min-height: 42px; padding: 8px 16px; box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--black); font-size: .96rem; }

  .btn-ifood { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .btn-ifood img { width: 58px; height: 24px; object-fit: contain; display: block; flex: 0 0 auto; }

  .gallery-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .gallery-item { min-height: 220px; border: 2px solid var(--black); border-radius: var(--radius); background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15,78,162,.12), rgba(255,250,240,.85)), radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(15,78,162,.22), transparent 55%); overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
  .gallery-item img { width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 220px; object-fit: cover; }
  .gallery-item figcaption { position: absolute; right: 12px; bottom: 12px; left: 12px; padding: 8px 10px; border: 1px solid var(--blue); background: rgba(255,250,240,.92); color: var(--black); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }

  .vip { border: 2px solid var(--blue); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 54px); background: rgba(255,250,240,.78); box-shadow: var(--shadow); text-align: center; }
  .vip p { max-width: 760px; margin: 18px auto 28px; font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif; font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.7vw, 1.14rem); font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.65; }

  .cta-strip { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; text-align: left; }
    .order-fries { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .order-actions { grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-content: center; }
  .cta-strip h2 { color: var(--blue); font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif; font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 5vw, 5rem); line-height: .88; letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .cta-strip p { color: var(--black); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.55rem); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1; text-transform: uppercase; }


  .order-bag {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 92px;
    height: 92px;
    border: 2px solid var(--blue);
    border-radius: 18px 18px 10px 10px;
    background: var(--paper-soft);
    position: relative;
  }

  .order-bag::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -18px;
    width: 42px;
    height: 28px;
    border: 5px solid var(--blue);
    border-bottom: none;
    border-radius: 26px 26px 0 0;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .order-bag img {
    width: 62px;
    height: 62px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 18%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }

  .order-copy {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .order-fries {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    align-self: end;
  }

  .order-fries img {
    width: min(160px, 100%);
    height: auto;
    max-height: 150px;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 8px rgba(17, 17, 17, .16));
  }

  .order-fries-fallback {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 118px;
    height: 112px;
    border: 2px solid var(--blue);
    border-radius: 8px 8px 20px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffaf0 0 38%, #f4f0e7 38% 100%);
    color: var(--blue);
    font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    position: relative;
  }

  .order-fries-fallback::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -38px;
    left: 16px;
    right: 16px;
    height: 48px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #f59d23 0 10px, transparent 10px 15px);
    border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
  }

  .order-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .order-action {
    min-height: 58px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 7px;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--black);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .order-action img {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .order-whatsapp {
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  .order-ifood {
    background: #d71920;
  }
  .site-footer { background: rgba(255,250,240,.7); border-top: 2px solid var(--black); }
  .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .75fr 1fr 1.2fr; gap: 30px; padding: 42px 0; }
  .footer-logo { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; min-width: 0; }
  .footer-logo .brand { min-width: 0; }
  .socials { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 18px; }
  .socials a {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--blue);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--paper-soft);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.14);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .socials a img {
    width: 25px;
    height: 25px;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
    transition: filter 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .socials a:hover,
  .socials a:focus-visible {
    transform: scale(1.08);
    border-color: transparent;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.18);
    outline: none;
  }

  .social-instagram:hover img,
  .social-instagram:focus-visible img,
  .social-ifood:hover img,
  .social-ifood:focus-visible img {
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .social-instagram:hover,
  .social-instagram:focus-visible {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f58529, #dd2a7b 45%, #8134af 72%, #515bd4);
  }

  .social-whatsapp:hover,
  .social-whatsapp:focus-visible {
    background: #25D366;
  }

  .social-ifood:hover,
  .social-ifood:focus-visible {
    background: #ea1d2c;
  }
  .footer-col h3 { margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--blue); font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif; font-size: 1.18rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }
  .footer-col li, .footer-col p { margin-bottom: 8px; font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif; font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.55; }
  .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }

  .fallback-logo { display: none; }

  .reveal, .reveal-left, .reveal-right { opacity: 0; transition: opacity .85s ease, transform .85s cubic-bezier(.22, 1, .36, 1); will-change: opacity, transform; }
  .reveal { transform: translateY(46px); }
  .reveal-left { transform: translateX(-48px); }
  .reveal-right { transform: translateX(48px); }
  .reveal-delay { transition-delay: .14s; }
  .reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: .26s; }
  .reveal.active, .reveal-left.active, .reveal-right.active { opacity: 1; transform: translate(0, 0); }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .reveal, .reveal-left, .reveal-right { opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: none; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .header-inner { min-height: 82px; }
    .menu-toggle { display: inline-grid; place-items: center; }
    .nav { position: fixed; inset: 82px 0 auto 0; display: none; flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; gap: 14px; padding: 22px 24px 28px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--black); background: var(--paper); box-shadow: 0 16px 24px rgba(17,17,17,.12); }
    body.menu-open .nav { display: flex; }
    .nav a, .nav .order-link { width: 100%; justify-content: center; text-align: center; }
    .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; align-items: start; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .hero-plate { min-height: 430px; }
    .hero-image-wrap { right: -28px; bottom: -10px; width: min(720px, 112%); height: 430px; }
    .products-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .product-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .product-info { padding: 20px; }
    .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .cta-strip { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; text-align: left; }
    .order-fries { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .order-actions { grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-content: center; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    body { font-size: 15.5px; }
    .container { width: min(100% - 24px, 1160px); }
    .logo-complete { height: 52px; max-width: 180px; }
    .brand-logo-fallback img { width: 52px; height: 52px; }
    .brand-name { font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px; }
    .brand-subtitle { font-size: .92rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px; }
    .hero { padding-top: 32px; }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(3.05rem, 14.5vw, 4.75rem); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: .98; }
    .eyebrow::before, .eyebrow::after { width: 28px; }
    .hero-actions { align-items: stretch; }
    .cta-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; justify-items: center; text-align: center; }
    .order-actions { width: 100%; flex-direction: column; }
    .order-action { width: 100%; }
    .order-fries { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .order-actions { grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-content: center; }
    .hero-actions .retro-button, .hero-actions .hero-badge, .cta-strip .retro-button, .vip .retro-button { width: 100%; }
    .hero-plate { min-height: 320px; }
    .hero-image-wrap { position: relative; right: auto; bottom: auto; width: 100%; height: 320px; }
    .hero-image-wrap .hero-main-image { object-position: center bottom; }
    .timeline { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 34px; }
    .timeline::before { top: 0; bottom: 0; left: 50%; right: auto; width: 3px; height: auto; }
    .timeline-item { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(247,241,231,.92), transparent); }
    .products-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .product-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .product-media { min-height: 220px; }
    .product-media img { height: 210px; }
    .product-info .retro-button { width: 100%; }
    .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
    .footer-logo, .footer-col { align-items: center; }
    .footer-logo .brand { justify-content: center; }
    .socials { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 18px; }
    .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    body { font-size: 15px; }
    .socials a { width: 48px; height: 48px; }
    .socials a img { width: 24px; height: 24px; }
    .container { width: min(100% - 20px, 1160px); }
    .header-inner { gap: 12px; }
    .logo-complete { height: 46px; max-width: 150px; }
    .menu-toggle { width: 44px; min-width: 44px; height: 44px; font-size: .9rem; }
    .nav { inset: 74px 0 auto 0; padding: 18px 16px 24px; }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 15.8vw, 3.9rem); letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: .98; }
    .section-title { font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 11vw, 3.35rem); letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .hero-copy { font-size: .98rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .hero-plate { min-height: 270px; }
    .hero-image-wrap { height: 270px; }
    .timeline-icon { width: 96px; height: 96px; font-size: 1.9rem; }
    .product-media img { height: 190px; }
    .vip, .cta-strip { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; text-align: left; }
    .order-fries { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .order-actions { grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-content: center; }
    .btn-ifood { gap: 8px; white-space: normal; }
    .btn-ifood img { width: 50px; height: 22px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    body { font-size: 15px; }
    .socials a { width: 48px; height: 48px; }
    .socials a img { width: 24px; height: 24px; }
    .whatsapp-float {
      right: 14px;
      bottom: 14px;
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
    }

    .whatsapp-float img {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
    }
  }

  /* Pedido: banner vintage horizontal */
  #peca-agora.cta-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto minmax(220px, .9fr) minmax(130px, .42fr) minmax(380px, 1fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(18px, 3vw, 34px);
    margin-top: 26px;
    padding: 20px 28px;
    border: 2px solid var(--blue);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: rgba(255, 250, 240, 0.86);
    text-align: left;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-fries,
  #peca-agora .order-actions {
    grid-column: auto;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-actions {
    width: auto;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-action {
    width: auto;
    color: #fff;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    #peca-agora.cta-strip {
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      text-align: left;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-fries,
    #peca-agora .order-actions {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #peca-agora.cta-strip {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      justify-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-actions {
      width: 100%;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-action {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  /* Ajuste final da seçăo Peça Agora */
  #peca-agora.cta-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto minmax(210px, .9fr) minmax(150px, .5fr) minmax(390px, 1.05fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(18px, 3vw, 32px);
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 18px 24px;
    border: 2px solid var(--blue);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(255, 250, 240, .92);
    text-align: left;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-bag {
    width: 94px;
    height: 92px;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-copy h2 {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.25rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    line-height: .86;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-copy p {
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.45rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-fries {
    grid-column: auto;
    align-self: center;
    justify-self: center;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-fries img {
    display: block;
    width: min(170px, 100%);
    max-height: 160px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 8px rgba(17, 17, 17, .16));
  }

  #peca-agora .order-actions {
    grid-column: auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    gap: 14px;
    width: auto;
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-action {
    width: auto;
    min-height: 58px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    color: #fff;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 7px;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--black);
    font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-action img {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    object-fit: contain;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-whatsapp {
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  #peca-agora .order-whatsapp img {
    filter: none;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-ifood {
    background: #d71920;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-ifood img {
    width: 70px;
    height: 30px;
    filter: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    #peca-agora.cta-strip {
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      text-align: left;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-fries,
    #peca-agora .order-actions {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-actions {
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #peca-agora.cta-strip {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      justify-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px 18px;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-bag {
      display: none;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-fries {
      grid-column: auto;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-actions {
      width: 100%;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    #peca-agora .order-action {
      width: 100%;
      white-space: normal;
    }
  }

  /* Batata integrada ao fundo do banner */
  #peca-agora .order-fries {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    box-shadow: none;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  #peca-agora .order-fries img {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    box-shadow: none;
    mix-blend-mode: normal;
    width: min(178px, 100%);
    max-height: 168px;
    object-fit: contain;
    object-position: center bottom;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 8px rgba(17, 17, 17, .14));
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #peca-agora .order-fries img {
      width: min(165px, 72vw);
      max-height: 158px;
    }
  }
  /* Correcao final: WhatsApp flutuante pequeno no canto superior esquerdo */
  .whatsapp-float {
    position: fixed !important;
    top: 106px !important;
    left: 20px !important;
    right: auto !important;
    bottom: auto !important;
    width: 58px !important;
    height: 58px !important;
    max-width: 58px !important;
    max-height: 58px !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    border-radius: 50% !important;
    background: #25d366 !important;
    display: flex !important;
    align-items: center !important;
    justify-content: center !important;
    overflow: hidden !important;
    z-index: 9999 !important;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22) !important;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease !important;
  }

  .whatsapp-float:hover {
    transform: scale(1.08) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.26) !important;
  }

  .whatsapp-float img {
    display: block !important;
    width: 32px !important;
    height: 32px !important;
    max-width: 32px !important;
    max-height: 32px !important;
    object-fit: contain !important;
    object-position: center !important;
    transform: none !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .whatsapp-float {
      top: 86px !important;
      left: 14px !important;
      width: 52px !important;
      height: 52px !important;
      max-width: 52px !important;
      max-height: 52px !important;
    }

    .whatsapp-float img {
      width: 29px !important;
      height: 29px !important;
      max-width: 29px !important;
      max-height: 29px !important;
    }
  }

  /* Clube Ship's: formulario para captacao via n8n */
  .club-card {
    width: min(920px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(24px, 4vw, 42px);
    border: 2px solid var(--blue);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: rgba(255, 250, 240, 0.76);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.07);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .club-card .section-title {
    margin: 10px auto 12px;
  }

  .club-copy {
    max-width: 660px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .club-form {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .club-field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 7px;
  }

  .club-field label {
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif;
    font-size: .92rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .club-field input {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.42);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.58);
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease;
  }

  .club-field input:focus {
    border-color: var(--blue);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(15, 78, 162, 0.13);
  }

  .club-form-actions {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .club-submit {
    min-height: 50px;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border: 2px solid var(--blue-dark);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--blue);
    color: #fff;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--black);
    transition: transform .22s ease, box-shadow .22s ease, background .22s ease;
  }

  .club-submit:hover {
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--black);
    background: var(--blue-dark);
  }

  .club-submit:disabled {
    cursor: wait;
    opacity: .72;
    transform: none;
  }

  .club-message {
    min-height: 24px;
    color: var(--blue);
    font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: .95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .club-message.error {
    color: #b51f1f;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .club-form {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .club-submit {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  /* Ajuste tipografico vintage: Ship's Burguer */
  body {
    font-family: "Roboto Slab", Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  h1,
  h2,
  h3,
  .brand-name,
  .section-title,
  .cta-strip h2 {
    font-family: "Rye", "Bebas Neue", serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 1.2px;
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3.55rem, 8.2vw, 6.85rem);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 1.04;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.15rem, 5.2vw, 3.7rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
  }

  .nav,
  .nav a,
  .retro-button,
  .nav .order-link,
  .menu-toggle,
  .eyebrow,
  .section-kicker,
  .hero-badge,
  .timeline-year,
  .timeline-item h3,
  .product-info h3,
  .price,
  .gallery-item figcaption,
  .cta-strip p,
  .footer-col h3,
  .club-field label,
  .club-submit,
  .order-action {
    font-family: "Oswald", Arial, sans-serif;
  }

  .hero-copy,
  .timeline-item p,
  .product-info p,
  .vip p,
  .club-copy,
  .club-field input,
  .club-message,
  .footer-col li,
  .footer-col p,
  .footer-bottom,
  p,
  li,
  input {
    font-family: "Roboto Slab", Georgia, serif;
  }

  .hero-copy,
  .timeline-item p,
  .product-info p,
  .vip p,
  .club-copy {
    line-height: 1.68;
  }

  .product-info h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 2.25vw, 1.95rem);
    letter-spacing: .8px;
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 2.05rem;
    letter-spacing: .8px;
  }

  .cta-strip h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.65rem, 4.3vw, 4.15rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  .brand-name {
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.2vw, 2.75rem);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.35rem, 11vw, 3.55rem);
      letter-spacing: .5px;
      line-height: 1.12;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 8.5vw, 3rem);
    }

    .cta-strip h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 10vw, 3.25rem);
    }

    .product-info h3 {
      font-size: 1.65rem;
    }
  }

  /* Ajuste final da hero/Nossa Historia: evita sobreposicao texto + imagem */
  .hero-grid {
    grid-template-columns: minmax(320px, 0.78fr) minmax(420px, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(34px, 5vw, 76px);
    align-items: end;
  }

  .hero-grid > div:first-child {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 590px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    max-width: 560px;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5.6vw, 5.65rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: .6px;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .hero-plate {
    min-height: 500px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-image-wrap {
    right: -34px;
    bottom: -10px;
    width: min(690px, 106%);
    height: min(510px, 70vw);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1180px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(300px, .9fr) minmax(380px, 1fr);
      gap: clamp(28px, 4vw, 54px);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      max-width: 520px;
      font-size: clamp(2.85rem, 5.2vw, 4.85rem);
    }

    .hero-image-wrap {
      right: -22px;
      width: min(620px, 104%);
      height: min(470px, 66vw);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .hero-grid > div:first-child,
    .hero h1,
    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.65rem, 8.6vw, 4.4rem);
      line-height: 1.12;
    }

    .hero-plate {
      min-height: 390px;
    }

    .hero-image-wrap {
      position: relative;
      right: auto;
      bottom: auto;
      width: 100%;
      height: 390px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.15rem, 9.8vw, 3.35rem);
      line-height: 1.16;
      letter-spacing: .3px;
    }

    .hero-plate {
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    .hero-image-wrap {
      height: 300px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.95rem, 9.2vw, 2.85rem);
      line-height: 1.18;
    }

    .hero-plate {
      min-height: 260px;
    }

    .hero-image-wrap {
      height: 260px;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#historia" aria-label="Ship's Burguer">
        <img class="logo-complete" src="images/Logo site" alt="Ship's Burguer" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline-flex';" />
        <span class="brand-logo-fallback">
          <img src="images/Shipinho.png" alt="Mascote Ship's Burguer" />
          <span class="brand-text">
            <span class="brand-name">Ship's</span>
            <span class="brand-subtitle">Burguer</span>
            <span class="brand-since">Since 2021</span>
          </span>
        </span>
      </a>

      <button class="menu-toggle" type="button" aria-label="Abrir menu" aria-expanded="false">Menu</button>

      <nav class="nav" aria-label="Menu principal">
        <a href="#historia">Nossa História</a>
        <a href="#lanches">Lanches</a>
        <a href="#galeria">Galeria</a>
        <a href="#grupo-vip">Grupo VIP</a>
        <a class="order-link" href="https://wa.me/5511976374369?text=Ol%C3%A1,%20vim%20pelo%20site%20da%20Ship%27s%20Burguer%20e%20quero%20fazer%20um%20pedido!" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Peça Agora</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="historia">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow reveal reveal-left">Nossa História</p>
          <h1 class="reveal reveal-left reveal-delay">Năo é só sobre burger. É sobre <span>história.</span></h1>
          <p class="hero-copy reveal reveal-left reveal-delay-2">
            Da nossa primeira chapa dentro de um trailer até a realizaçăo do sonho da loja própria.
            Essa é a história da Ship's Burguer: feita de determinaçăo, família, clientes que viraram amigos
            e uma vontade enorme de servir o melhor burger da regiăo.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions reveal reveal-left reveal-delay-2">
            <a class="retro-button" href="#trajetoria">Conheça nossa jornada</a>
            <span class="hero-badge">Ship's Burguer desde 2021</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-plate" aria-label="Burger artesanal da Ship's Burguer">
          <div class="hero-image-wrap reveal reveal-right">
            <img class="hero-main-image" src="images/copo com o shipinho.png" alt="Hambúrguer e copo com Shipinho" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="trajetoria">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading reveal">
          <p class="section-kicker">Nossa trajetória</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Uma história feita de <span>determinaçăo</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline">
          <article class="timeline-item reveal">
            <div class="timeline-icon" aria-hidden="true">21</div>
            <strong class="timeline-year">2021</strong>
            <h3>O começo</h3>
            <p>Tudo começou em um pequeno trailer, com muita vontade de fazer o melhor burger da regiăo.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="timeline-item reveal reveal-delay">
            <div class="timeline-icon" aria-hidden="true">22</div>
            <strong class="timeline-year">2022</strong>
            <h3>Crescendo</h3>
            <p>A qualidade conquistou clientes e nossa fama só aumentava. O trailer ficou pequeno perto do sonho.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="timeline-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="timeline-icon" aria-hidden="true">23</div>
            <strong class="timeline-year">2023</strong>
            <h3>Uma família</h3>
            <p>Mais que clientes, conquistamos amigos. A Ship's Burguer virou ponto de encontro.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="timeline-item reveal">
            <div class="timeline-icon" aria-hidden="true">24</div>
            <strong class="timeline-year">2024</strong>
            <h3>A realizaçăo</h3>
            <p>O sonho se tornou realidade: nossa loja física nasceu para oferecer uma experięncia ainda melhor.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="lanches">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading reveal">
          <p class="section-kicker">Nossos destaques</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Lanches</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="products-grid">
          <article class="product-card reveal">
            <div class="product-media">
              <img src="smash-guilbert.png" alt="Smash Guilbert" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550547660-d9450f859349?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop';" />
            </div>
            <div class="product-info">
              <h3>Smash Guilbert</h3>
              <p>Smash, queijo derretido, alface, tomate, maionese especial e crispy de cebola.</p>
              <strong class="price">R$ 27,90</strong>
              <a class="retro-button" href="https://wa.me/5511976374369?text=Ol%C3%A1,%20vim%20pelo%20site%20da%20Ship%27s%20Burguer%20e%20quero%20fazer%20um%20pedido!" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Peça Agora</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product-card reveal reveal-delay">
            <div class="product-media">
              <img src="smash-toven.png" alt="Smash Toven" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594212699903-ec8a3eca50f5?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop';" />
            </div>
            <div class="product-info">
              <h3>Smash Toven</h3>
